Content:: Stefan Bissegger (born 13 September 1998)[2] is a Swiss professional road and track racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI WorldTeam EF Education–EasyPost.[3] He rode in the men's individual pursuit event at the 2018 UCI Track Cycling World Championships.[4]  This biographical article relating to Swiss cycling is a stub.
